date: 20120514
brief instruction on how to compile & run the ipe

go to the directory where makefile is located
$ cd src

Depending on your shell, set up the environment by doing one of the following:
$ source setup_ipe.zeus.tcsh
$ source setup_ipe.jet.tcsh
$ source setup_ipe.jet.lahey.tcsh
$ source setup_ipe.jet.bash

clean before compile 
$ make cln

compile serial
$ make
compile parallel
$ make PAR=sms

go to the run directory
cd ../run
copy the desired IPE.inp.* into IPE.inp

run the executable
$ ../src/ipe.v18.exe

or submit a job:
#For zeus:
$ qsubipe
#For JET
$ qsubipejET
